Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:58.91,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}You think we're different
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:01.79,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}You think we never feel the way you do
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:04.29,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}We've got scars to prove we're too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:06.17,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Nothing but human
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:08.84,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Fueled by emotions that we thought we knew
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.84,0:01:11.34,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}But really had no clue
